T1  - Avoiding High Opportunism Is Easy, Achieving Low Opportunism Is Not: A QCA Study on Curbing Opportunism in Buyer–Supplier Relationships
AU  - Mellewigt, Thomas
AU  - Hoetker, Glenn
AU  - Lütkewitte, Martina
Y1  - 2018/10/24
